reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars VERY cheap... but works surprisingly great!
reviews.reviewText: I honestly didn't think this shoe rack would work since it seems so flimsy, but it actually works great lolOne thing - it is pretty rough, so if you have young kids who get into things... you're going to have a LOT of splinters.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Used in entry way
reviews.reviewText: The shoe rack, so far, is pretty good. Very easy to assemble (4 screws) and doesn't take up a lot of room in the entry way. However, I don't think I will place heavy shoes on it because I'm not sure how much weight it can actually hold. But for now it is fine and the cost was low.
